><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.asianavenue.com/indiegrrl/faedrake.JPG WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> The Definitive Equipment Upgrade Post</span><hr size=1> OK, the EIGHT most recently posted threads in this forum are equipment upgrade threads.  And it's getting really, really old posting the same things over and over.  With this in mind, here is the definitive progression for levels 30-55ish of &quot;what you should upgrade to.&quot;  Listed in roughly ascending order of quality ... a slash (/) indicates the items are roughly equivalent and should be selected based on personal preference.  Feel free to add to this list!  And yes, I know other ugprades than the ones I've listed exist; I've simply listed what I personally think are the best options for the particular price/level range.<br>
<br>
Ears: Gold Jasper -&gt; Forest Loop -&gt; Electrum Black Sapphire / Electrum Blue Diamond / Earring of Essence<br>
Head: Runed Circlet / Lumberjack's Cap -&gt; Crown of the Froglok Kings / Tranix<br>
Neck: Chrysoberyl Talisman / Black Alloy Medallion / Bone Amulet of Blade Turning / Warden Symbol of Tunare -&gt; Velium Black Sapphire / Rough Silver Chain<br>
Face: Velium Ruby Veil -&gt; Polished Mithril Mask / Bone Mask of the Jarsath -&gt; Enshrouded Veil<br>
Rings: Velium Jasper -&gt; Diamond Wedding Band / Golem Tear / Velium Jade / Velium Fire Opal / Coldain Insignia<br>
Wrists: CBBs -&gt; RMBs -&gt; Verm / Coldain Military Wristguard / Bracer of Hammerfal / Velious Quest<br>
Hands: Splitpaw -&gt; Gnomeskin -&gt; ES -&gt; Cured Tizmak -&gt; Coldain Skin / Crystal Chitin<br>
Arms: Hollowed Bone Bracers -&gt; Ulthork Hide -&gt; Giant Scalemail / ES -&gt; Crystal Chitin<br>
Shoulders: Lizardscale -&gt; Braided Ivy Cords -&gt; Tattered Mantle / Prayer Shawl / Meditative Blanket -&gt; Obulus Death Shroud / Coldain Shawl<br>
Chest: Ulthork / Tizmak -&gt; Mithril Runed Tunic -&gt; Tree Weave / Shroud of Nature<br>
Waist: Thick Leather Apron / Straw Spun Belt -&gt; Blood Wolf Harness -&gt; Crystalline Belt / Crested BW Harness -&gt; Mucilaginous Girdle / Reed / Dweamorvine / Oakleaf / Cobalt Drake<br>
Back: Kunzar -&gt; Cloak of the Ry`Gorr Oracles / Mammoth Hide -&gt; Heirophant's / Lodizal<br>
Legs: Gatorscale -&gt; Kromriff Military -&gt; Gladiator Chain<br>
Feet: Burynai / Vale / Mithril -&gt; Golden Efreeti / Coldain Skin -&gt; Shimmering Terror Hide -&gt; Crystal Chitin / Barbed Dragonscale<br>
Primary: Velium Etched Stone Mace -&gt; Sharkbone Warhammer / Springwood Club / Spirit Tome -&gt; Cone of the Mystics / Paw of Opolla -&gt; epic<br>
Secondary: Testament / Crystal Webshield -&gt; Charred Guardian Shield -&gt; Sarnak Battle Shield<br>
Range: Small Wisdom Deity -&gt; Medicine Totem -&gt; Frozen Orb / Seal of Thoridain / Idol of the Thorned -&gt; Talisman of Benevolence<br>
