<i>Soldier of Tunare</i><br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umugwye.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mugwye</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(7/26/01 6:32:33 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Int does not help raise trade skills (at least for druids)</span><hr size=1> &quot;The +5Int is also nice in raising skill level for trade skills and so forth. &quot;  <br>
